We provide two equivalent installation algoritms.

=============  1. CMAKE  ==============

Cmake simplifies package installation on various platforms 
Visit http://www.cmake.org for more details.

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../
$ make install


=============  2. MAKEFILEs  ===============

We created simplified Makefiles in every directory. 
Type 'make help' for more details.

$ vi src/Rules.make 
provide correct names and options for FORTRAN and C compilers 

$ make libs
$ make packages


Illustration of package capabilities is discribed in README.


